5265  Npp64f * pCoeffs; /* device memory pointer to the tranformation matrix with double precision floating-point coefficient values to be used for this image */
5266  Npp64f aTransformedCoeffs[3][3]; /* FOR INTERNAL USE, DO NOT INITIALIZE */
5267 } NppiWarpPerspectiveBatchCXR;
